; Regression test for issue #611:
; --trace must not trigger an assertion failure when journal files use
; the include directive.  The instance_parse timer was restarted with
; a different description (containing the new filename) and start_timer()
; asserted that the description matched the original, causing a crash.
;
; This test verifies that included files are parsed correctly.  The
; underlying fix is in start_timer() which now updates the timer
; description instead of asserting an exact match.

2024/01/01 Main Payee
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

include 611.dat

2024/02/01 Another Payee
    Expenses:Food    $15.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-50.00  Assets:Cash
              $50.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
